4. Linear Regression Model¶

Now, I will check whether there is a relationship between like ratio and some known variables: time since publishment, category id, rating_disabled, comments_disabled¶

  • category_id cannot be used in model as is, it should be transformed to dummy variables
In [110]:
category_df = pd.DataFrame(pd.get_dummies(US_df['category_id']))

  • input & target dataframe preparation

model inputs selected: 'days_difference','comments_disabled','ratings_disabled', 'category_id', 'channel_title'

variables like views, likes, dislikes cannot be used for prediction because their values are unknown till the time comes
